r\">Celer\u003C/span>\u003C/span> · pater · eṭ [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"author":3,"date":4,"citedRange":283,"ptr":284,"ref":285,"inscriptionDate":4,"title":2,"citation":5,"uri":6,"year":4},"44 c",{"target":136},{"_":138,"target":138},{"file":287,"uri":287,"title":288,"status":289,"editionAuthor":13,"type":290,"objectType":294,"material":296,"condition":308,"layoutDesc":309,"handNote":314,"date":328,"places":332,"geo":335,"country":70,"provenance":67,"provenanceGeo":337,"region":81,"settlement":2,"repository":338,"idno":339,"textLang":341,"tmNumber":343,"facsimile":344,"letterHeights":348,"publications":356,"zotero":358,"keywords":360,"html":365,"bibl":366,"bulletinDateSort":139,"citedRangeSort":367,"languageSort":90,"materialSort":297,"typeSort":291},"ISic000656","Honorific inscription for Sextus Pompeius Priscus",{"_":12},{"_":291,"ana":292,"ref":293},"funerary","#function.funerary","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html",{"_":19,"ana":20,"ref":295},"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/259",{"_":297,"ana":298,"type":25,"subtype":299,"resp":30,"ref":31,"placeName":301},"Coarse-grained, banded, white marble, likely Naxian. Digital microscopy: heteroblastic fabric. ND only: banded, he, coarse (identification based on pXRF, digital microscopy)\n","#material.inorganic.stone.metamorphic_rock.marble.calcitic_marble.Naxian",[300],"Naxian",{"type":302,"ref":303,"location":306},"provenance",{"_":304,"target":305},"Tyros, Greece","https://www.geonames.org/256631/nisi-naxos.html",{"geo":307},"37.07257,25.48616",{"ana":236},{"layout":310},{"p":311,"rs":312,"damage":313},"Three lines of Latin text in straight alignment. Line 1 has a larger module than Line 2, and Line 2 has a larger module than Line 3. Furthermore, the lack of space in the final line resulted in a greater compression between the letters compared to the other lines.",{"_":38,"ana":39,"ref":40},{"ana